sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant KFP as KFP API Server
    participant InitC as Init Container<br/>(odh-pipelines-components)
    participant SharedVol as Shared Volume<br/>(/config/managed-pipelines)
    participant ArgoWF as Argo Workflow<br/>(Pipeline Runner)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Trainer as Training Workers<br/>(GPU Pods)
    participant PVC as PVC Workspace<br/>(ReadWriteMany)
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack API<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLM as vLLM<br/>(Local GPU)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over InitC,SharedVol: Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Staging (Platform Startup)
        InitC->>InitC: generate_managed_pipelines.py<br/>Compile pipeline.py → YAML
        InitC->>SharedVol: Copy compiled YAMLs<br/>+ managed-pipelines.json manifest
        KFP->>SharedVol: Read managed pipeline YAMLs<br/>Serve to users
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 2: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (LoRA/OSFT/SFT)
        User->>KFP: Submit fine-tuning pipeline
        KFP->>ArgoWF: Create Argo Workflow

        ArgoWF->>HF: GET dataset (HF_TOKEN)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>ArgoWF: Dataset files
        ArgoWF->>S3: GET dataset (AWS IAM)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        S3-->>ArgoWF: Dataset files
        ArgoWF->>PVC: Write preprocessed data

        ArgoWF->>K8sAPI: POST TrainingJob CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI->>Trainer: Schedule GPU worker pods
        Trainer->>PVC: Read training data
        Trainer->>Trainer: Train model (LoRA/OSFT/SFT)
        Trainer->>PVC: Write model checkpoints
        Trainer-->>ArgoWF: Training complete

        ArgoWF->>vLLM: Load model for evaluation
        vLLM-->>ArgoWF: Evaluation metrics (MMLU, GSM8K, etc.)

        ArgoWF->>ModelReg: POST model metadata<br/>HTTP/8080 (plaintext, no auth)
        ModelReg-->>ArgoWF: Model version registered
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoRAG pipeline
        KFP->>ArgoWF: Create Argo Workflow

        ArgoWF->>S3: LIST + GET documents<br/>AWS IAM, HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        S3-->>ArgoWF: Documents (PDF, DOCX, etc.)
        ArgoWF->>ArgoWF: Docling text extraction<br/>(local processing)

        ArgoWF->>LlamaStack: POST search space models<br/>API key auth, TLS
        LlamaStack-->>ArgoWF: Available models list

        ArgoWF->>LlamaStack: POST vector store indexing<br/>+ RAG inference calls
        LlamaStack-->>ArgoWF: Optimization results

        ArgoWF->>ArgoWF: Leaderboard evaluation<br/>(local pattern.json scoring)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over User,PVC: Flow 4: AutoML Tabular Training Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoML pipeline
        KFP->>ArgoWF: Create Argo Workflow

        ArgoWF->>S3: GET CSV data (streaming)<br/>AWS IAM, HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        S3-->>ArgoWF: CSV data stream
        ArgoWF->>PVC: Write train/test splits

        ArgoWF->>ArgoWF: AutoGluon model training<br/>(local CPU processing)
        ArgoWF->>PVC: Write trained models + metrics

        ArgoWF->>ArgoWF: Leaderboard evaluation<br/>(model comparison)
    end
